headline: Castrol Unveils "The Engine" Paint Scheme in Crossover Partnership Ahead of 2025 AT&T WNBA All-Star Game
summary: Castrol, a global leader in lubricant technology and the Official Motor Oil Partner of the NBA and WNBA, today unveiled a one-of-a-kind paint scheme for RFK Racing in a crossover partnership that brings together several high-profile platforms ahead of the 2025 AT&T WNBA All-Star Game. Inspired by six-time WNBA All-Star Alyssa "The Engine" Thomas, the livery design celebrates the relentless drive for excellence and a collective commitment to performance.
